ensities up to a bit less than $2$ meters at the largest one considered in\nthis work, $0.3$ fm$^{-3}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Jun 2022 08:47:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-05"}
